summary: Completed comprehensive testing of Sistema de Gestión Vehicular Naval for Ecuadorian Navy. All backend APIs and frontend functionality working perfectly with 120 mock vehicles and realistic Ecuadorian data.
passed_tests: Dashboard KPIs display (flota operativa 63.3%, 8 alertas críticas)
Dashboard charts render (pie, bar, line charts)
GPS map displays 120 vehicle markers with Ecuador locations
All navigation pages accessible (Alertas, Combustible, Reportes, Configuración)
Backend API /api/kpis returns complete KPI data
Backend API /api/vehiculos returns 120 vehicles with Ecuadorian plates
Backend API /api/alertas returns alerts by severity
Vehicle detail pages with maintenance/fuel history
Statistics endpoints for consumption and maintenance
